17
00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:35.360
What I'd like to do tonight is go through the individual apps I use,

18
00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:39.460
one by one, looking at how they work,

19
00:01:39.460 --> 00:01:44.460
or rather what the apps can do these days.

20
00:01:44.460 --> 00:01:50.460
And what settings I've adjusted in some cases,

21
00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:50.500
just to give you a better overview.

22
00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:57.460
Just to give you a better overview, and at the end

