40
00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:34.500
So this is the first one.

41
00:03:34.500 --> 00:03:40.540
Windy — most of you already know it.

42
00:03:40.540 --> 00:03:45.540
Before we go into the Windy app itself,

43
00:03:45.540 --> 00:03:49.540
I'd like to show you the settings

44
00:03:49.540 --> 00:03:52.540
I'd recommend you change,

45
00:03:52.540 --> 00:03:55.540
