46
00:03:55.540 --> 00:03:58.540
And generally also for the wind.

47
00:03:58.540 --> 00:04:01.540
I use km/h, temperature in Celsius,

48
00:04:01.540 --> 00:04:03.540
and pressure in hectopascals.

49
00:04:03.540 --> 00:04:07.540
Just basic settings here,

50
00:04:07.540 --> 00:04:12.020
under the menu point up at the top right,

51
00:04:12.020 --> 00:04:14.020
