54
00:04:21.020 --> 00:04:27.020
Wind animation normal or high.

55
00:04:27.020 --> 00:04:29.020
High is okay.

56
00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:32.020
The higher it is,

57
00:04:32.020 --> 00:04:34.500
the more I feel

58
00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:36.500
it gets cluttered,

59
00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:40.500
the density I mean, the density.

60
00:04:40.500 --> 00:04:43.500
The higher you set the density, the more

61
00:04:43.500 --> 00:04:47.500
yeah, the more cluttered it gets, just try it out.

62
00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:54.500
But if you set the animation to high

63
00:04:54.500 --> 00:04:57.780
and the density a bit higher,

64
00:04:57.780 --> 00:05:00.780
